===同行評論===
[[File:FIFA_WC-qualification_2014_-_Austria_vs._Germany_2012-09-11_-_Toni_Kroos.JPG|thumb]]於69秒內攻入兩球，成為世界盃歷史上最快梅開二度的球員。他於賽後表示巴西隊盡了他們的努力，但同時認為他們並不在最佳狀態<ref name=kroos/>。]] 

懸殊的賽果引起了球圈的震驚。因傷而未能出戰的巴西前鋒[[尼馬|-{zh-hk:尼馬;zh-tw:內馬爾;zh-cn:内马尔;}-]]在家通過電視直播觀看這場比賽，當比數擴大至7比0時，他選擇關上電視並去打撲克牌<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.rp-online.de/sport/fussball/wm/andere-teams/neymar-konnte-beim-17-debakel-nicht-hinschauen-aid-1.4378913 |title=Neymar Konnte Beim Debakel Nicht Hinschauen Aid |date=2014-07-10 |accessdate=2014-07-14 |publisher=MRP (German) |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140713214413/http://www.rp-online.de/sport/fussball/wm/andere-teams/neymar-konnte-beim-17-debakel-nicht-hinschauen-aid-1.4378913 |archivedate=2014-07-13 }}</ref>。領隊[[路易斯·菲利佩·斯科拉里|-{zh-hans:斯科拉里;zh-hk:史高拉利;zh-tw:斯科拉里;}-]]於賽後稱這是巴西隊有史以來「最慘烈的敗仗」以及他人生中「最難過的一天」，為承擔球隊落敗的責任，他會於世界盃完結後辭退<ref>{{cite news |last=Fifield |first=Dominic |url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/2014/jul/09/brazil-luiz-felipe-scolari-germany-world-cup |title=Brazil's Luiz Felipe Scolari accepts blame after hammering by Germany |date=2014-07-09 |accessdate=2014-07-09 |publisher=The Guardian |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140709094644/http://www.theguardian.com/football/2014/jul/09/brazil-luiz-felipe-scolari-germany-world-cup |archivedate=2014-07-09 }}</ref>。代替-{zh-hk:施華;zh-tw:席爾瓦;zh-cn:席爾瓦;}-出任隊長的後衛[[大衛·雷斯|-{zh-hans:大卫·路易斯;zh-hk:大衛·雷斯;zh-tw:大衛·路易斯;}-]]和門將[[儒利奥·塞萨尔|-{zh-hans:儒利奥·塞萨尔;zh-hk:祖利奧·施薩;zh-tw:儒利奧·塞薩爾;}-]]於賽後向巴西民眾道歉<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/28222679 |title=Brazil captain David Luiz apologises after loss |date=2014-07-09 |accessdate=2014-07-09 |publisher=BBC |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140709024345/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/28222679 |archivedate=2014-07-09 }}</ref>。被主場支持者報以噓聲的[[佛雷德里科·查韦斯·格德斯|-{zh-hans:弗雷德;zh-hk:費特;zh-tw:佛雷德;}-]]說這球場是他和隊友們經歷過最大的失利，他在世界盃落幕後宣佈退出國家隊<ref>{{cite news|title=Fred retires from international football|url=http://en.espn.co.uk/football/sport/story/323875.html|accessdate=2014-07-14|publisher=[[ESPN|ESPN]]|date=2014-07-13|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150613161059/http://en.espn.co.uk/football/sport/story/323875.html|archivedate=2015-06-13}}</ref>。傷癒復出後，-{zh-hk:尼馬;zh-tw:內馬爾;zh-cn:内马尔;}-表示會繼續支持其隊友，並對作為國家隊成員一份子引以自豪<ref>{{cite news|title=Neymar : " J'aurais pu finir en chaise roulante " [Neymar: I could have ended up in a wheelchair]|url=http://www.lemonde.fr/coupe-du-monde/video/2014/07/11/neymar-j-aurais-pu-finir-en-chaise-roulante_4455384_1616627.html|work=Le Monde|date=2014-07-11|language=fr|accessdate=2018-06-09|archive-date=2020-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200713114046/https://www.lemonde.fr/coupe-du-monde/video/2014/07/11/neymar-j-aurais-pu-finir-en-chaise-roulante_4455384_1616627.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

另一方面，德國隊在半場取得5比0的巨大優勢後則選擇踢得比較收斂。後衛[[麥斯·曉姆斯|-{zh-hans:胡梅尔斯;zh-hk:曉姆斯;zh-tw:胡梅爾斯;}-]]向記者表示這是隊友們於中場休息時決定的：「我們說得很清楚，在下半場比賽的時候會我們保持對比賽的專注度，而不是去刻意羞辱他們。你必須要尊敬你的對手，我們也沒有認為打出這樣的比分就是非常重要的，重要的是我們打好自己的比賽」<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.nydailynews.com/sports/soccer/germany-vowed-not-humiliate-brazil-world-cup-semifinal-hummels-article-1.1861976 | title = Germany made halftime pledge not to further humiliate Brazil in World Cup semifinal, says Mats Hummels | date = 2014-07-10 | work = New York Daily News | accessdate = 2016-07-09 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160817113116/http://www.nydailynews.com/sports/soccer/germany-vowed-not-humiliate-brazil-world-cup-semifinal-hummels-article-1.1861976 | archivedate = 2016-08-17 }}</ref>。儘管如此，德國隊是在下半場取得兩個入球，但球員們僅高舉雙臂慶祝，並沒有跳跃或大叫<ref name=oziltweet>{{cite web | url = http://www.ibtimes.com/after-7-1-destruction-brazil-classy-germans-tweet-support-losers-1623424 | title = After 7-1 Destruction Of Brazil, Classy Germans Tweet Support For The Losers | date = 2014-07-09 | work = International Business Times | publisher =  | accessdate = 2014-07-17 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140713081650/http://www.ibtimes.com/after-7-1-destruction-brazil-classy-germans-tweet-support-losers-1623424 | archivedate = 2014-07-13 }}</ref>。領隊[[约阿希姆·勒夫|-{zh-hans:勒夫;zh-hk:路維;zh-tw:勒夫;}-]]指球隊有「明確而堅決的戰術佈署」，而之所以出現大勝是因為巴西球員在落後方寸大亂，德國隊則「處之泰然」所致<ref name=ind>{{cite news |last=Wallace |first=Sam |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/international/brazil-vs-germany-world-cup-2014-we-had-a-clear-persistent-gameplan-says-germany-coach-joachim-low-after-comprehensive-victory-9593529.html |title='We had a clear, persistent game-plan,' says Germany coach Joachim Low after comprehensive victory |date=2014-07-09 |accessdate=2014-07-09 |publisher=The Independent |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141030072037/http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/international/brazil-vs-germany-world-cup-2014-we-had-a-clear-persistent-gameplan-says-germany-coach-joachim-low-after-comprehensive-victory-9593529.html |archivedate=2014-10-30 }}</ref>。獲選為本場比賽最佳球員的[[托尼·克罗斯|-{zh-hans:托尼·克罗斯;zh-hk:東尼·卻奧斯;zh-tw:托尼·克羅斯;}-]]認為巴西隊盡了他們的努力，而球隊的致勝關鍵是基於出色的控球和能夠把握入球機會<ref name=kroos>{{cite web|url=http://www.superesportes.com.br/app/1,1195/2014/07/08/interna-noticia,288218/kroos-aponta-brasil-aquem-de-seu-futebol-na-copa-e-diz-sentir-pena-por-goleada.shtml|title=Kroos aponta Brasil aquém de seu futebol na Copa e diz sentir pena por goleada|publisher=Superesportes (Diários Associados)|author=Andrade, Gustavo|date=2014-07-08|accessdate=2015-05-04|language=pt|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518104415/http://www.superesportes.com.br/app/1,1195/2014/07/08/interna-noticia,288218/kroos-aponta-brasil-aquem-de-seu-futebol-na-copa-e-diz-sentir-pena-por-goleada.shtml|archivedate=2015-05-18}}</ref>。雖然取得大捷，-{zh-hans:勒夫;zh-hk:路維;zh-tw:勒夫;}-表示球員不會因此得意忘形，並會專注於接下來的決賽<ref>{{cite web |last=McCarthy |first=Barbara |url=http://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/opinion/news-analysis/joachim-lows-heroes-have-inspired-me-to-be-a-bit-more-german-30437351.html |title=Joachim Low's heroes have inspired me to be a bit more German |work=Belfast Telegraph |date=2014-07-17 |accessdate=2014-08-03 |archive-date=2020-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200711152003/https://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/opinion/news-analysis/joachim-lows-heroes-have-inspired-me-to-be-a-bit-more-german-30437351.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

德國人賽後向巴西給予安慰。-{zh-hans:勒夫;zh-hk:路維;zh-tw:勒夫;}-、[[佩尔·默特萨克|-{zh-hans:默特萨克;zh-hk:梅迪薩卡;zh-tw:默特薩克;}-]]和[[菲利普·拉姆|-{zh-hans:菲利普·拉姆;zh-hk:拿姆;zh-tw:拉姆;}-]]稱對巴西於半決賽出局的心情表示理解，因德國也曾以東道主身份在[[2006年國際足協世界盃|2006年世界盃]]的半決賽止步<ref>{{cite web |url=http://trivela.uol.com.br/selecao-alema-deu-exemplo-de-elegancia-ao-confortar-os-brasileiros-apos-goleada/ |title=Seleção alemã deu exemplo de elegância com brasileiros |date=2014-07-08 |accessdate=2014-07-10 |publisher=Trivela |language=pt |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140715002149/http://trivela.uol.com.br/selecao-alema-deu-exemplo-de-elegancia-ao-confortar-os-brasileiros-apos-goleada/ |archivedate=2014-07-15 }}</ref>。-{zh-hans:菲利普·拉姆;zh-hk:拿姆;zh-tw:拉姆;}-及後在訪問中補充在這場比賽過程中他因巴西隊連接犯錯而落敗感到「並不好過」且「不覺高興」<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.stern.de/sport/fussball/wm-2014/philipp-lahm-im-stern-das-71-gegen-brasilien-war-beklemmend-2124641.html |title=Das 7:1 gegen Brasilien war "beklemmend" |date=2014-07-17 |accessdate=2014-07-28 |publisher=Stern |language=de |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140724230619/http://www.stern.de/sport/fussball/wm-2014/philipp-lahm-im-stern-das-71-gegen-brasilien-war-beklemmend-2124641.html |archivedate=2014-07-24 }}</ref>。-{zh-hans:勒夫;zh-hk:路維;zh-tw:勒夫;}-相信巴西隊在這場比賽受盡外來壓力而失準，故希望他們能夠忘記失利，以捲土重來<ref>{{cite web|url=http://veja.abril.com.br/noticia/esporte/toni-kroos-atropelou-o-brasil-e-depois-disse-sentir-pena/|title=Toni Kroos atropelou o Brasil. E depois disse sentir 'pena'|date=2014-07-08|author=Lepiani, Giancarlo|work=Veja|accessdate=2015-05-04|language=pt|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151002070807/http://veja.abril.com.br/noticia/esporte/toni-kroos-atropelou-o-brasil-e-depois-disse-sentir-pena/|archivedate=2015-10-02}}</ref>。

巴西一代球王[[比利|-{zh-cn:贝利;zh-hk:比利;zh-tw:比利}-]]於[[Twitter|Twitter]]中寫道：「我不時說足球是充滿驚喜的盒子，沒有人能預計到會出現這樣的賽果」，又相信巴西隊能在[[2018年國際足協世界盃|來屆的世界盃]]第6度問鼎冠軍<ref name=espnfc>{{cite web|title=Germany 7–1 World Cup semi-final win over Brazil breaks Twitter record with 35.6M tweets – ESPN FC|url=http://www.espnfc.com/league-name/story/1940689/headline|publisher=ESPN FC|accessdate=2014-07-09|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006083718/http://www.espnfc.com/league-name/story/1940689/headline|archivedate=2014-10-06}}</ref>。前國家隊隊長[[卡洛斯·阿尔贝托|-{zh-hans:卡洛斯·阿尔贝托;zh-hk:卡路士·阿爾拔圖;zh-tw:卡洛士‧阿爾貝托}-]]指「球員們以為冠軍已是囊中之物」終使得球隊大敗收場，並讚揚德國隊的發揮以及批評-{zh-hans:斯科拉里;zh-hk:史高拉利;zh-tw:斯科拉里;}-的戰術安排「猶如自殺」<ref>{{cite news |last1=Kallás |first1=Fernando |title=Carlos Alberto: "La táctica de Scolari fue un suicidio" [Carlos Alberto "Scolari's tactics were suicidal"] |url=http://futbol.as.com/futbol/2014/07/09/mundial/1404913885_330302.html |date=2014-07-09 |accessdate=2014-07-09 |work=Diario AS |language=es |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140709234848/http://futbol.as.com/futbol/2014/07/09/mundial/1404913885_330302.html |archivedate=2014-07-09 }}</ref>。1994年冠軍隊主力前鋒[[羅馬里奧|羅馬里奧]]對賽果感到憤怒，斥責於本場比賽中上陣的八成巴西球員是球隊「永遠的傷疤」，而且「不配再穿上國家隊球衣」，並將這場慘敗歸咎於[[巴西足球協會|巴西足球協會]]的腐敗無能<ref>{{cite news |last1=Kallás |first1=Fernando |title=罗马里奥：八成巴西队员该开除 永不配再穿黄衫 |url=http://2014.sohu.com/20140714/n402183005.shtml |date=2014-07-14 |accessdate=2014-07-14 |work=搜狐 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150328091433/http://2014.sohu.com/20140714/n402183005.shtml |archivedate=2015-03-28 }}</ref>。阿根廷領隊薩維利亞對宿敵巴西的大敗抱以同情，稱「足球就是不可理喻的」<ref>{{cite web |last=Kent |first=David |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/worldcup2014/article-2685404/Argentina-boss-Alejandro-Sabella-loss-explain-Brazils-World-Cup-humiliation-Germany.html |title=Argentina boss Alejandro Sabella at a loss to explain Brazil's World Cup humiliation by Germany |publisher=Dailymail.co.uk |date=2013-09-17 |accessdate=2014-07-11 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140709124925/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/worldcup2014/article-2685404/Argentina-boss-Alejandro-Sabella-loss-explain-Brazils-World-Cup-humiliation-Germany.html |archivedate=2014-07-09 }}</ref>。不過，同樣來自阿根廷的名宿[[迭戈·马拉多纳|-{zh-hans:马拉多纳;zh-hant:馬拉度納;zh-tw:馬拉度納;zh-hk:馬勒當拿}-]]則在賽後唱歌譏笑巴西的大敗<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.foxnews.com/sports/2014/07/11/maradona-sings-song-mocking-brazil-7-1-loss-to-germany-in-world-cup-semifinals/ |title=Maradona sings song mocking Brazil's 7-1 loss to Germany in World Cup semifinals |publisher=Fox News |date=2014-07-11 |accessdate=2014-08-03 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140809012614/http://www.foxnews.com/sports/2014/07/11/maradona-sings-song-mocking-brazil-7-1-loss-to-germany-in-world-cup-semifinals/ |archivedate=2014-08-09 }}</ref>。

===社會===
[[File:Dilma_Rousseff_-_foto_oficial_2011-01-09.jpg|thumb]]於賽後在Twitter上表示對失利「非常非常難過」。]]

在德國，[[德國電視二台|德國電視二台]]直播這場賽事，最終共吸引3.257億人收看，[[收視率|收視率]]為87.8%，是該國歷史以來最多人觀看的電視節目<ref>{{cite web |last=Mantel |first=Uwe |url=http://www.dwdl.de/zahlenzentrale/46626/deutschland_jubelt_sich_zum_allzeitquotenrekord/ |title=Deutschland jubelt sich zum Allzeit-Quotenrekord |publisher=DWDL |date=2014-07-09 |accessdate=2014-07-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714125329/http://www.dwdl.de/zahlenzentrale/46626/deutschland_jubelt_sich_zum_allzeitquotenrekord/ |archivedate=2014-07-14 }}</ref>。這紀錄於5日後的決賽再被刷新。與高歌凱進的德國相反，在巴西則是一次次刺痛，每當德國隊取得入球時，這比賽的觀看人數而隨之下滑<ref>{{cite web|url=http://noticiasdatv.uol.com.br/noticia/copa-na-tv/vexame-do-brasil-na-copa-do-mundo-tem-pior-audiencia-na-globo-4048|title=Vexame do Brasil na Copa do Mundo tem pior audiência na Globo|language=pt|publisher=UOL|date=2014-07-08|accessdate=2014-07-10|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140711080847/http://noticiasdatv.uol.com.br/noticia/copa-na-tv/vexame-do-brasil-na-copa-do-mundo-tem-pior-audiencia-na-globo-4048|archivedate=2014-07-11}}</ref>。本場比賽驚人的賽果也引起互聯網上的熱議。比賽舉行當天，全球共發出了3.56億條[[Twitter|推文]]，這超越了[[第四十八屆超級盃|第48屆超級盃]]2.49億條推文的紀錄<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.com/news/blogs-trending-28226010 |title=#BBCtrending: Brazil's World Cup thrashing breaks Twitter records |date=2014-07-09 |accessdate=2014-07-09 |work=BBC Online |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140709134627/http://www.bbc.com/news/blogs-trending-28226010 |archivedate=2014-07-09 }}</ref> 。當巴西隊在開賽初段落後時，巴西觀眾臉上已經難掩失落，[[主題標籤|主題標籤]]多以「#替巴西祈禱」（#PrayForBrazil）為主。然而，當球隊被攻入五球，巴西用戶開始從沮喪變成自嘲，以諷刺球隊差勁的表現<ref>{{cite news |url=http://impresso.em.com.br/app/noticia/cadernos/superesportes/2014/07/09/interna_superesportes,121314/sem-perder-o-humor.shtml |title=Sem perder o humor |work=Estado de Minas |language=pt |last=Pacelli |first=Shirley |date=2014-07-09 |registration=yes |accessdate=2018-06-09 |archive-date=2021-02-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210214203314/https://digital.em.com.br/flip-login/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。另一方面，Twitter用戶對德國完全控制比賽的局面感到驚嘆，將球隊類比作[[第二次世界大戰|第二次世界大戰]]時的德軍<ref>{{cite web |url=http://nymag.com/daily/intelligencer/2014/07/nazi-holocaust-jokes-during-germany-brazil-world-cup.html |title=Twitter Sure Does Have a Lot of Nazi and Holocaust Jokes for the Germany-Brazil Game! |date=2014-07-08 |accessdate=2014-07-10 |work=New York |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140709135403/http://nymag.com/daily/intelligencer/2014/07/nazi-holocaust-jokes-during-germany-brazil-world-cup.html |archivedate=2014-07-09 }}</ref>。大量經修改的圖片被網民轉載，比如各種數字的變形、[[基督山|基督山]]上的[[基督像|基督像]]在痛哭以及德國隊門將因巴西隊久久沒有攻門而坐下來看書，這些圖片也被轉發上萬次<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/sports/2014/07/140709_wc2014_twitter |title=巴西隊世界杯慘敗引爆推特發帖記錄 |date=2014-07-09 |accessdate=2014-07-10 |work=BBC |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180610121228/http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/sports/2014/07/140709_wc2014_twitter |archivedate=2018-06-10 }}</ref>。國家隊的大敗還引起巴西民眾對政府和總統[[迪爾瑪·羅塞夫|迪爾瑪·羅塞夫]]的不滿。早在世界盃展開前，民眾就對政府為舉辦賽事而動用大量資金興建球場感到不快<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.vox.com/2014/7/10/5882275/world-cup-loss-brazil-germany-dilma-rousseff-election |title=Could Brazil's epic World Cup loss cost its president her job? |date=2014-07-10 |accessdate=2014-07-10 |work=Vox |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140713065720/http://www.vox.com/2014/7/10/5882275/world-cup-loss-brazil-germany-dilma-rousseff-election |archivedate=2014-07-13 }}</ref>。隨著巴西隊的大敗，民眾的不滿情緒更為明顯。在比賽結束後，大量巴西人咒罵羅塞夫下地獄<ref>{{cite web |url=http://2014.sohu.com/20140710/n402055027.shtml |title=巴西贝洛大屠杀球迷矛头直指政客 政府紧急救火 |date=2014-07-10 |accessdate=2014-07-10 |work=搜狐 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180610121229/http://2014.sohu.com/20140710/n402055027.shtml |archivedate=2018-06-10 }}</ref>。為平息民憤，羅塞夫於Twitter上致歉：「和大家一樣，我對失利非常非常難過，我對你們所有人表示十分抱歉」<ref>{{cite news|title=Dilma lamenta derrota e diz que sente pelos jogadores e por brasileiros|trans-title=Dilma laments the defeat and says that she feels for the players and for the Brazilians|url=http://oglobo.globo.com/brasil/dilma-lamenta-derrota-diz-que-sente-pelos-jogadores-por-brasileiros-13184906|accessdate=2015-10-21|work=O Globo|date=2014-07-08|language=pt|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714035803/http://oglobo.globo.com/brasil/dilma-lamenta-derrota-diz-que-sente-pelos-jogadores-por-brasileiros-13184906|archivedate=2014-07-14}}</ref>。

這場比賽讓巴西人聯想起「[[馬拉簡拿之痛|馬拉簡拿之痛]]」。「馬拉簡拿之痛」是指[[1950年國際足協世界盃|1950年世界盃]]上東道主巴西成功躋身決賽，該決賽由四支球隊進行單循環比賽，最終積分居首的即為冠軍。巴西於首兩輪賽事獲勝，他們只需要餘下對烏拉圭的比賽中守和即可奪標。然而，巴西最終以1比2失利，失落冠軍。此後，「馬拉簡拿之痛」標誌著巴西足球史上的恥辱。在本場賽事中，巴西同樣以主辦國的身份遭到大敗，故該國傳媒稱這敗仗為「明尼路之痛」<ref name="FIFANumbers"/>。於「馬拉簡拿之痛」擔任門將的是阿西尔·巴博萨，其女兒指父親成為比賽失利的代罪羔羊，民眾亦把其畢生的功勞抹煞<ref name=globe>{{cite web|url=https://www.theglobeandmail.com/sports/soccer/world-cup/brazil-losers-on-the-field-now-turn-to-the-blame-game/article19524752/|title=Brazil, losers on the field, now turn to the blame game|work=The Globe and Mail|date=2014-07-09|accessdate=2014-09-01|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150715055820/http://www.theglobeandmail.com/sports/soccer/world-cup/brazil-losers-on-the-field-now-turn-to-the-blame-game/article19524752/|archivedate=2015-07-15}}</ref>。於「馬拉簡拿之痛」攻進致勝入球的[[阿爾基得斯·吉賈|阿爾基得斯·吉賈]]認為「馬拉簡拿之痛」和「明尼路之痛」也為巴西人民帶來了心理創傷，但前者造成的傷害較大<ref>{{cite web|url=http://esportes.estadao.com.br/noticias/futebol,copa-do-mundo,maracanazo-e-diferente-porque-foi-final-lembra-ex-jogador-ghiggia,1526087|title="O Maracanazo é diferente porque foi uma final", afirma Ghiggia|publisher=Agência EFE|work=Estado de S. Paulo|date=2014-07-09|accessdate=2014-09-01|language=pt|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140813060430/http://esportes.estadao.com.br/noticias/futebol,copa-do-mundo,maracanazo-e-diferente-porque-foi-final-lembra-ex-jogador-ghiggia,1526087|archivedate=2014-08-13}}</ref>。

雖然遭到大敗，但是人們似乎處於震驚中，在巴西的各個城市大致還是比較平靜，只出現零星騷動。在[[里約熱內盧|里約熱內盧]]，有黑幫趁機搶劫，而在[[聖保羅_(巴西)|聖保羅]]則有市民在比賽結束前燒[[巴西國旗|巴西國旗]]和巴士泄憤<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2014/07/09/sports/worldcup/world-cup-2014-host-brazil-stunned-7-1-by-germany-in-semifinal.html|title=Goal, Goal, Goal, Goal, Goal, Goal, Goal: A Dark Day for Brazil|date=2014-07-09|accessdate=2014-07-09|publisher=New York Times|registration=yes|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140708230841/http://www.nytimes.com/2014/07/09/sports/worldcup/world-cup-2014-host-brazil-stunned-7-1-by-germany-in-semifinal.html|archivedate=2014-07-08}}</ref><ref name="busesablaze">{{cite web | url = http://www.sbs.com.au/news/article/2014/07/09/buses-set-ablaze-after-brazils-world-cup-loss | title = Buses set ablaze after Brazil's World Cup loss | publisher = SBS | date = 2014-07-09 | accessdate = 2014-09-05 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141005050547/http://www.sbs.com.au/news/article/2014/07/09/buses-set-ablaze-after-brazils-world-cup-loss | archivedate = 2014-10-05 }}</ref>。另外，為防止賽後出現的足球流氓暴力洩憤，會方召集了防暴警察，保護進場觀賽的德國球迷安全，當晚並護送他們離開球場<ref>{{cite news |author=work |url=http://www.cbc.ca/m/touch/world/story/1.2700432 |title=CBC News – World Cup 2014: Brazil fans stunned as Germany routs home team |publisher=Cbc.ca |date=2014-07-09 |accessdate=2014-07-09 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141120160425/http://www.cbc.ca/m/touch/world/story/1.2700432 |archivedate=2014-11-20 }}</ref>。報導還指，其實離場當下德國人在賽後仍鼓勵東道主的球迷，表現出尊重與打氣的態度，反之死對頭阿根廷同是南美國家，在巴西觀賽的支持者則大肆慶祝和嘲笑巴西的慘敗<ref name="sports.yahoo.com"/><ref>{{cite web |last=Espejel |first=Denisse |url=https://news.vice.com/article/riots-in-buenos-aires-after-argentinas-world-cup-final-defeat |title=Riots in Buenos Aires After Argentina's World Cup Final Defeat |publisher=VICE News |date=2014-07-14 |accessdate=2014-08-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402101950/https://news.vice.com/article/riots-in-buenos-aires-after-argentinas-world-cup-final-defeat |archivedate=2015-04-02 }}</ref>。

===傳媒===
比賽翌日，巴西的主流報章均以慘敗作為封面報導。《Lance!》以「史上最大恥辱」為大字標題，《[[聖保羅頁報|聖保羅頁報]]》稱這是「歷史性的恥辱」，而《世界報》則感嘆巴西「已被殺死」<ref name="bbc">{{cite web |title=How the world reacted to Brazil's humiliation |url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/28223121 |date=2014-07-09 |accessdate=2014-07-10 |publisher=BBC Sport |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140709114203/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/28223121 |archivedate=2014-07-09 }}</ref>。德國的《[[圖片報|圖片報]]》以「瘋狂的7比1」為標題，法國的《[[隊報|隊報]]》則以「災難」來形容巴西隊的潰敗<ref name="bbc"/>。英國的《[[天空體育|天空體育]]》宣稱比賽令人感到「異常的尷尬」，並相信巴西人需要多年時間才能忘記這場比賽<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www1.skysports.com/football/news/15241/9376285/a-night-that-will-never-be-forgotten |title=A World Cup night for Brazil that will never be forgotten |date=2014-07-08 |accessdate=2014-07-09 |work=Sky Sports |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141018051750/http://www1.skysports.com/football/news/15241/9376285/a-night-that-will-never-be-forgotten |archivedate=2014-10-18 }}</ref>。美國的《[[ESPN|ESPN]]》指強大的巴西隊遭到如斯慘敗實在令人難以置信，同時表揚德國隊傑出的表現<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.espnfc.com/blog/the-match/60/post/1940261/three-points-history-made-as-brazil-broken-by-rampant-germany |title=Three points: Brazil left broken |date=2014-07-09 |accessdate=2014-07-09 |publisher=ESPN |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140712084647/http://www.espnfc.com/blog/the-match/60/post/1940261/three-points-history-made-as-brazil-broken-by-rampant-germany |archivedate=2014-07-12 }}</ref>。

此外，英國的《[[衛報|衛報]]》指巴西隊的這場大敗是世界盃主辦國歷來最慘烈的敗仗，《[[獨立報|獨立報]]》認為這是巴西足球史上最黑暗的一夜<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/blog/2014/jul/09/brazil-world-cup-humiliation-germany-should-serve-call-arms |title=Brazil World Cup humiliation by Germany should serve as a call to arms |date=2014-07-09 |accessdate=2014-07-09 |publisher=The Guardian |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140710012451/http://www.theguardian.com/football/blog/2014/jul/09/brazil-world-cup-humiliation-germany-should-serve-call-arms |archivedate=2014-07-10 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/international/brazil-vs-germany-analysis-world-cup-2014-joachim-lows-golden-generation-into-world-cup-final-and-can-finally-shine-9593395.html |title=Joachim Low's golden generation into World Cup final and can finally shine |date=2014-07-08 |accessdate=2014-07-09 |publisher=The Independent |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141029071304/http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/international/brazil-vs-germany-analysis-world-cup-2014-joachim-lows-golden-generation-into-world-cup-final-and-can-finally-shine-9593395.html |archivedate=2014-10-29 }}</ref>。《[[BBC|BBC]]》駐里約熱內盧的記者指這場比賽後所有的巴西人都埋沒在震驚和尷尬之中<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-latin-america-28223461|title=Shock and humiliation in Brazil after German rout|date=2014-07-09|publisher=BBC News|last=Davies|first=Wyre|accessdate=2014-07-09|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140709140157/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-latin-america-28223461|archivedate=2014-07-09}}</ref>。足球記者提姆·韋利認為巴西一直沉醉於過去輝煌的歷史，忽視與列強的實力差距已日漸縮少終至大敗而回，故希望巴西隊經歷這次慘敗後能重新審視與各國的水平差距，以作以部署<ref>{{cite web |last=Vickery |first=Tim |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/28223138 |title=Brazil must learn lessons from Germany humiliation |date=2014-07-09 |publisher=BBC News |accessdate=2014-07-09 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140709144119/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/28223138 |archivedate=2014-07-09 }}</ref>。

事實上，巴西傳媒曾試圖從戰術和用人等方面分析球隊大敗的原因。《聖保羅頁報》指-{zh-hans:路易斯·菲利佩·斯科拉里;zh-hk:雷斯·菲臘比·史高拉利;zh-tw:斯科拉里;}-在這場比賽使用的球員大多為[[2013年洲際國家盃|-{zh-hans:2013年洲际国家杯;zh-hant:2013年洲際國家盃;zh-cn:2013年国际足联联合会杯;zh-hk:2013年國際足協洲際國家盃}-]]的一員，但他們要麼不在狀態，要麼未曾踢過世界盃<ref name=fsp>{{cite web|url=http://temas.folha.uol.com.br/7-a-1-um-ano-depois/introducao/felipao-vai-de-pai-do-penta-a-gestor-do-fracasso.shtml|date=2015-07-08|language=pt|title=Felipão vai de pai do penta a gestor do fracasso|author1=Itri, Bernardo|author2=Rizzo, Marcel|work=Folha de S. Paulo|accessdate=2015-09-05|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150803011734/http://temas.folha.uol.com.br/7-a-1-um-ano-depois/introducao/felipao-vai-de-pai-do-penta-a-gestor-do-fracasso.shtml|archivedate=2015-08-03}}</ref>。此報還指出球隊過份依賴[[尼馬|-{zh-hk:尼馬;zh-tw:內馬爾;zh-cn:内马尔;}-]]，一旦他缺陣球隊的攻力則大為下降<ref name=fsp/>。另外，為解決因[[尼馬|-{zh-hk:尼馬;zh-tw:內馬爾;zh-cn:内马尔;}-]]未能上陣下攻力下降的問題，-{zh-hans:路易斯·菲利佩·斯科拉里;zh-hk:雷斯·菲臘比·史高拉利;zh-tw:斯科拉里;}-派出前鋒[[伯纳德·阿尼西奥·卡尔德拉·杜阿尔特|-{zh-cn:伯纳德;zh-hk:伯拿特;zh-tw:伯納德}-]]上陣，此舉被《聖保羅頁報》批評是錯的，該報主張面對德國隊強大的中場時更應增添中場力量才是「理性的」<ref name=fsp/>。其它國家的評論員也有類似見解，英國《[[每日郵報|每日郵報]]》認為巴西隊於當屆世界盃的表現並不理想，不論在分組賽和兩場淘汰賽均艱辛地取勝，當在半決賽面對強大的德國隊時自然相形見絀<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/worldcup2014/article-2685745/Brazils-7-1-defeat-Germany-World-Cup-semi-final-ended-fairytale-started-believe-in.html|title=Brazil's 7-1 defeat by Germany in the World Cup semi-final showed just how deep their flaws were... they were always likely to be on the end of this kind of hiding|work=The Daily Mail|date=2014-07-09|accessdate=2014-09-05|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140819193651/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/worldcup2014/article-2685745/Brazils-7-1-defeat-Germany-World-Cup-semi-final-ended-fairytale-started-believe-in.html|archivedate=2014-08-19}}</ref>。《[[每日電訊報|每日電訊報]]》也指出巴西隊的中場力量不足使得德國隊的[[托尼·克罗斯|-{zh-hans:克罗斯;zh-hk:卻奧斯;zh-tw:克羅斯;}-]]、[[萨米·赫迪拉|-{zh-hans:赫迪拉;zh-tw:凱迪拉;zh-hk:基迪拉;}-]]和[[巴斯蒂安·施魏因斯泰格|-{zh-hans:施魏因斯泰格;zh-hk:舒韋恩史迪加;zh-tw:史汪斯泰格;}-]]能輕鬆地壓抑巴西隊的中場線<ref name=tel>{{cite web|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/teams/brazil/11310460/Brazil-1-Germany-7-The-World-Cup-match-that-will-echo-down-the-years-to-the-shame-of-hosts-proud-history.html|title=Brazil 1 Germany 7: The World Cup match that will echo down the years to the shame of host's proud history|work=The Telegraph|date=2014-12-24|accessdate=2015-09-05|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150824173328/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/teams/brazil/11310460/Brazil-1-Germany-7-The-World-Cup-match-that-will-echo-down-the-years-to-the-shame-of-hosts-proud-history.html|archivedate=2015-08-24}}</ref>，賽前巴西隊的助教也曾提議過要以防守較佳的[[威廉·伯格斯·达·席尔瓦|威廉]]或[[拉美利斯|拉米雷斯]]來填補內馬爾的位子。《[[衛報|衛報]]》分析指-{zh-hans:路易斯·菲利佩·斯科拉里;zh-hk:雷斯·菲臘比·史高拉利;zh-tw:斯科拉里;}-未有另外使用球員換走表現不佳的後衛[[大衛·雷斯|-{zh-hans:大卫·路易斯;zh-hk:大衛·雷斯;zh-tw:大衛．路易斯;}-]]和[[丹特_(足球运动员)|-{zh-cn:丹特; zh-tw:丹特; zh-hk:丹迪;}-]]是巴西兵敗如山倒的主因<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/2014/dec/30/looking-back-at-germany-v-brazil-world-cup-semi-final|title=Looking back at Germany v Brazil, World Cup semi-final|work=The Guardian|date=2014-12-30|accessdate=2015-09-05|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150906215048/http://www.theguardian.com/football/2014/dec/30/looking-back-at-germany-v-brazil-world-cup-semi-final|archivedate=2015-09-06}}</ref>，其中丹特前幾場表現顯然不及席爾瓦，而先前表現不差的路易斯在這場接手隊長職位卻是讓人意想不到的犯了許多低級失誤：主要是他常常進行一些賭博式的長傳以及多次拋下自己原本看防的球員去包夾持球者，多次導致隊伍失去球權或者布陣大亂。美國《[[CNN|CNN]]》另外指出邊後衛[[马塞洛·维埃拉|-{zh-hans:马塞洛;zh-hk:馬些路;zh-tw:馬塞洛;}-]]承擔進攻任務使巴西隊的防守更為薄弱、[[路易斯·古斯塔沃|-{zh-hans:古斯塔沃;zh-hk:古斯達禾;zh-tw:古斯塔沃;}-]]在[[马塞洛·维埃拉|-{zh-hans:马塞洛;zh-hk:馬些路;zh-tw:馬塞洛;}-]]參與進攻時沒有辦法一個人處理過大的防區：德國隊在克洛澤進球後，把左翼厄齊爾調到右路來對馬塞洛的防區施壓，而巴西隊的後防球員們並沒有立刻對此次變陣做出反應，這是導致他們六分鐘內連掉四球的最大原因。另外，角色定位不明確的[[佛雷德里科·查韦斯·格德斯|-{zh-hans:弗雷德;zh-hk:費特;zh-tw:佛雷德;}-]]（他的長處在於能協助多種戰術的運作，但不是像內馬爾一般能長時間持球和防守球員對峙並突破的前鋒）欠佳的進攻表現也是巴西隊大敗的成因<ref name="news18">{{cite web|url=http://www.news18.com/footballnext/news/world-cup-2014-five-reasons-why-brazil-lost-to-germany-700580.html|title=World Cup 2014: Five reasons why Brazil lost to Germany|author=Raghav Chopra|publisher=CNN-News18|date=2014-07-09|accessdate=2016-06-27|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160813142405/http://www.news18.com/footballnext/news/world-cup-2014-five-reasons-why-brazil-lost-to-germany-700580.html|archivedate=2016-08-13}}</ref>。

==後續==
巴西隊於本場賽事後的4日與[[荷蘭國家足球隊|荷蘭]]爭取季軍，最終以0比3失利，僅獲殿軍<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.smh.com.au/fifa-world-cup-2014/world-cup-match-report/world-cup-2014-netherlands-pile-more-misery-on-brazil-in-third-place-playoff-20140713-zt5so.html |title=World Cup 2014: Netherlands pile more misery on Brazil in third place play-off |work=Sydney Morning Herald |date=2014-07-13 |accessdate=2014-07-15 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140715042216/http://www.smh.com.au/fifa-world-cup-2014/world-cup-match-report/world-cup-2014-netherlands-pile-more-misery-on-brazil-in-third-place-playoff-20140713-zt5so.html |archivedate=2014-07-15 }}</ref>。巴西隊於整屆世界盃賽事中一共丟掉14球，是歷次參加世界盃以來失球最多的一次，也是繼[[比利時國家足球隊|比利時]]於[[1986年國際足協世界盃|1986年世界盃]]失15球後，失球最多的球隊<ref name="FoxBraNed">{{cite web |url=http://www.foxsports.com/soccer/story/netherlands-claim-third-place-in-world-cup-add-brazil-misery-match-report-071214 |title=Netherlands add to Brazil's misery, claim third place in World Cup |publisher=Fox Sports |date=2014-07-12 |accessdate=2014-07-13 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140721020718/http://www.foxsports.com/soccer/story/netherlands-claim-third-place-in-world-cup-add-brazil-misery-match-report-071214 |archivedate=2014-07-21 }}</ref>。另一方面，德國隊於[[2014年國際足協世界盃決賽|決賽]]以1比0小勝[[阿根廷國家足球隊|阿根廷]]，奪得冠軍。這是德國自[[兩德統一|統一]]後的首個世界盃冠軍，也是包括西德時期以來的第四個冠軍<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/2014/jul/13/germany-argentina-world-cup-final-2014-match-report |title=Germany 1-0 Argentina (aet) |work=The Guardian |date=2014-07-13 |accessdate=2014-07-15 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714232459/http://www.theguardian.com/football/2014/jul/13/germany-argentina-world-cup-final-2014-match-report |archivedate=2014-07-14 }}</ref> 。儘管德國隊曾大勝巴西，但考慮到不想宿敵阿根廷奪冠，加上德國隊在7比1賽後仍講求運動精神的態度，巴西人在決賽期間是普遍支持德國隊的<ref name="sports.yahoo.com"/>。

巴西隊先後於半決賽及季軍賽連接落敗，是1940年後第一次遭逢主場兩連敗<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.livesoccertv.com/news/10710/brazil-s-3-0-loss-to-netherlands-spells-first-consecutive-home-defeat-since-1940/ |title=Brazil's 3-0 loss to Netherlands spells first consecutive home defeats since 1940 |publisher=Live Soccer TV |date=2014-07-13 |accessdate=2014-08-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140730232203/http://www.livesoccertv.com/news/10710/brazil-s-3-0-loss-to-netherlands-spells-first-consecutive-home-defeat-since-1940/ |archivedate=2014-07-30 }}</ref>。7月15日，巴西領隊-{zh-hans:路易斯·菲利佩·斯科拉里;zh-hk:雷斯·菲臘比·史高拉利;zh-tw:路易斯·菲利佩·斯科拉里;}-辭去職務<ref>{{cite news|title=Luiz Felipe Scolari: Brazil coach resigns after 2014 World Cup|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/28289452|accessdate=2014-07-18|work=BBC Sport|date=2014-07-15|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140717123535/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/28289452|archivedate=2014-07-17}}</ref>。兩星期後，巴西足球協會宣佈會由[[鄧加|鄧加]]接任<ref name=yahoo>{{cite web |url=https://esportes.yahoo.com/blogs/soccer-dirty-tackle/brazil-brings-back-dunga--might-be-pretending-the-2014-world-cup-never-happened-192657813.html?showMessage=1 |title=Brazil brings back Dunga, might be pretending the 2014 World Cup never happened |publisher=Yahoo! Sports |date=2014-07-22 |accessdate=2014-08-03 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141215072859/https://esportes.yahoo.com/blogs/soccer-dirty-tackle/brazil-brings-back-dunga--might-be-pretending-the-2014-world-cup-never-happened-192657813.html?showMessage=1 |archivedate=2014-12-15 }}</ref>。這是他第二次執教巴西隊，此前他曾在2006年至2010年期間手持教鞭，直至球隊於[[2010年國際足協世界盃|2010年世界盃]]八強不敵荷蘭出局<ref name=yahoo />。他後來在2016年的[[百年美洲盃|百年美洲盃]]中因未能帶領巴西隊於分組賽出線而再次離職<ref>{{cite web|title=Dunga sacked as Brazil head coach following Copa America exit|url=http://www.skysports.com/football/news/12027/10313956/dunga-sacked-as-brazil-head-coach-following-copa-america-exit|publisher=Sky Sports|date=2016-06-16|accessdate=2016-09-18|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160917134718/http://www.skysports.com/football/news/12027/10313956/dunga-sacked-as-brazil-head-coach-following-copa-america-exit|archivedate=2016-09-17}}</ref>。

由於巴西對德國的大敗，第二日的四強賽事[[荷蘭國家足球隊|荷蘭]]對[[阿根廷國家足球隊|阿根廷]]時雙方都比之前的比賽踢得比較保守。結果雙方連加時共120分鐘都互無紀錄，最終阿根廷在互射十二碼階段以4-2淘汰荷蘭晉級決賽。

